'''Kraznys mo Nakloz''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 3|third season]]. He is a slave-trader in the city of [[Astapor]], on the coast of [[Slaver's Bay]], and one of the [[Good Masters]], the ruling elite of the city. He is an immensely wealthy individual who has grown rich from the training and trading of the [[Unsullied]] warrior-eunuchs.

